        {
          "type": "explanation",
          "name": "ATTN - Modders",
          "definition": "Set both map and campaign id to -1 for any levels which are not MCC's built-in levels. For UGC maps, the scenario field above is used to resolve the level's map guid at runtime via the associated .mapinfo (when using tools) or from what MCC dynamically feeds the engine via the level's mapinfo json file."
